      "originalText": "Repositories: WeDOTalent/recruiter_agent_v5 (Python/FastAPI) · WeDOTalent/ats_api (Rails 7.1) · WeDOTalent/ats_front (Nuxt 3/Vue 3) · WeDOTalent/ats_mcp (Node.js MCP)\nPlataforma LIA (Replit) — Next.js/React prototyping environment for PM validation before production implementation",
